Subject: [PATCH 0348/1115] ARM: OMAP2+: AM43x: determine features

Determine AM43x device features by reusing AM335x helper as feature
register layout is similar.

Signed-off-by: Afzal Mohammed <afzal@ti.com>
(cherry picked from commit 254eb7a5f129a38448720db7727aa8b0f94ec729)
Signed-off-by: Zumeng Chen <zumeng.chen@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/mach-omap2/io.c |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/mach-omap2/io.c b/arch/arm/mach-omap2/io.c
index bf76e70..d6c07d1 100644
--- a/arch/arm/mach-omap2/io.c
+++ b/arch/arm/mach-omap2/io.c
@@ -608,6 +608,7 @@ void __init am43xx_init_early(void)
 	omap_prm_base_init();
 	omap_cm_base_init();
 	omap3xxx_check_revision();
+	am33xx_check_features();
 	am43xx_powerdomains_init();
 	am43xx_clockdomains_init();
 	am33xx_hwmod_init();
